				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\boldsymbol{\omega}$\end{document} on a uniform hexahedral grid. Then, one must analyse 3×3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
