Rotating motions of plasma at the feet of quiescent prominence were also detected by Orozco Suárez et al. (2012) in the line of He i 10830 Å observed with the GREGOR Infrared Spectropolarimeter (GRIS, Collados et al. 2012). These persistently rotative motions had a LOS Doppler velocity equal to 6kms−1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
